    "• The design, modeling, simulation, fabless manufacturing, packaging, and test ecosystem will start to mature, bringing a new cohort of engineers and increased access.",
    "A shorter fabrication turnaround will further expedite the R&D.",
    "• Plasma-dispersion-based modulators will continue to serve adequately for many WDM communication applications, but at the same time, Pockels modulators and phase shifters will be commercialized in the SOI CMOS processes.",
    "LNOI will be integrated with silicon photonics processes for applications that require very high-speed modulation and low V π, despite their longer dimensions that prohibit LSI/VLSI integration.",
    "• Likewise, high-efficiency thermo-optical heaters will not be pushed out overnight."
